crypto

Class Pair<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • crypto.Pair<T>

  • public class Pair<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a 2-tuple (or pair) of BigInteger values. This is useful for representing ElGamal ciphers. These pairs are not mutable. This was adapted from DSW's original "Tuple" class.
